    <main id="main-content">
        <!-- Hero Section -->
        <section class="issue-hero" style="background-image: url('assets/images/placeholder-hero.jpg');">
            <div class="issue-hero-overlay"></div>
            <div class="container">
                <div class="issue-hero-content">
                    <h1>Office of the National Cyber Director</h1>
                    <p class="issue-hero-description">Protecting doll data, securing digital infrastructure, and defending against cyber threats in our connected world.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Overview Section -->
        <section class="issue-overview-section">
            <div class="container">
                <div class="issue-overview-content">
                    <h2>Mission Statement</h2>
                    <p>The Office of the National Cyber Director (ONCD) serves as the principal advisor to the President on cybersecurity policy and strategy. In an increasingly digital world where dolls rely on technology for everything from dreamhouse automation to career advancement, cybersecurity has never been more critical.</p>
                    <p>ONCD coordinates the federal government's efforts to protect critical infrastructure, secure sensitive doll data, and defend against cyber threats from malicious actors. We work across government agencies, with private sector partners, and with international allies to create a safer, more secure digital ecosystem for all dolls.</p>
                    <p>Our office develops comprehensive cybersecurity strategies, coordinates incident response, promotes best practices, and ensures that as technology advances, security keeps pace. We're committed to protecting the digital infrastructure that powers modern doll life while preserving privacy and civil liberties.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Key Initiatives -->
        <section class="initiatives-section">
            <div class="container">
                <h2>Key Focus Areas</h2>
                <div class="initiatives-grid">
                    <div class="initiative-card">
                        <span class="initiative-icon">🔐</span>
                        <h3>Critical Infrastructure Protection</h3>
                        <p>Securing essential systems including power grids, dreamhouse networks, and communication infrastructure from cyber threats.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="initiative-card">
                        <span class="initiative-icon">🛡️</span>
                        <h3>Data Security</h3>
                        <p>Protecting sensitive doll information, personal data, and government systems through robust security measures and encryption.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="initiative-card">
                        <span class="initiative-icon">🚨</span>
                        <h3>Incident Response</h3>
                        <p>Coordinating rapid response to cyber incidents and attacks, minimizing damage and restoring services quickly.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="initiative-card">
                        <span class="initiative-icon">🤝</span>
                        <h3>Public-Private Partnership</h3>
                        <p>Collaborating with tech companies, businesses, and organizations to share threat intelligence and best practices.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="initiative-card">
                        <span class="initiative-icon">📚</span>
                        <h3>Cybersecurity Education</h3>
                        <p>Promoting cyber awareness and training programs to help all dolls protect themselves online and build cyber skills.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="initiative-card">
                        <span class="initiative-icon">🌐</span>
                        <h3>International Cooperation</h3>
                        <p>Working with allied nations to combat global cyber threats and establish international cybersecurity norms.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Leadership Section -->
        <section class="priority-areas-section">
            <div class="container">
                <h2>Leadership</h2>
                <div class="priority-block">
                    <h3>National Cyber Director</h3>
                    <p>The National Cyber Director is appointed by the President and confirmed by the Senate, serving as the principal cybersecurity advisor within the Executive Office of the President. The Director leads efforts to protect and secure federal networks and critical infrastructure from evolving cyber threats.</p>
                    <p>Working closely with national security agencies, the Director of National Intelligence, and the Secretary of Homeland Security, the National Cyber Director coordinates whole-of-nation cyber defense and resilience efforts.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="priority-block">
                    <h3>Strategic Priorities</h3>
                    <p>ONCD's strategy focuses on defending critical infrastructure, disrupting malicious cyber actors, shaping market forces to improve security, and investing in a resilient future. These priorities guide our efforts to build a cyber-secure nation where innovation can flourish safely.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Impact Statistics -->
        <section class="impact-stats-section">
            <div class="container">
                <h2>Cybersecurity Impact</h2>
                <div class="stats-grid">
                    <div class="stat-card">
                        <span class="stat-number">99.9%</span>
                        <span class="stat-label">Infrastructure Uptime</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="stat-card">
                        <span class="stat-number">10M+</span>
                        <span class="stat-label">Threats Blocked Daily</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="stat-card">
                        <span class="stat-number">500K</span>
                        <span class="stat-label">Cyber Professionals Trained</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="stat-card">
                        <span class="stat-number">24/7</span>
                        <span class="stat-label">Monitoring & Response</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

